154
00:09:48,900 --> 00:09:49,870
Hey.

155
00:09:50,780 --> 00:09:53,200
This is your only chance to stop.

156
00:09:57,100 --> 00:09:59,140
Good luck, Hayate!

157
00:10:01,160 --> 00:10:02,460
This is amazing.

158
00:10:02,460 --> 00:10:03,970
I can't miss a frame of this.

159
00:10:03,970 --> 00:10:05,880
I really think he should stop.

160
00:10:08,450 --> 00:10:10,600
Ready, everyone?!

161
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:12,110
You will, Jac***?

162
00:10:12,110 --> 00:10:13,390
Jump, Jac***!

163
