166
00:10:32,930 --> 00:10:36,360
I never imagined I'd find film this old.

167
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:40,690
In this networked world, it's hard to recall movies that once got distributed.

168
00:10:40,690 --> 00:10:41,850
