Su-Sukinan dakara, mou.

170
00:10:44,480 --> 00:10:46,820
Su-Sukinan dakara, mou. = Y-You really like this kind of stuff.

171
00:10:49,210 --> 00:10:52,110
Ureshinakijya, boke!

172
