Ureshinakijya, boke! = We're crying because we're happy, you idiot!

173
00:10:52,110 --> 00:10:54,930
Hakuou Academy Motion Picture Research Club. The First...

174
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:55,800
...Exciting...

175
00:10:55,800 --> 00:10:58,770
...Normal Story Competition!

176
00:10:59,330 --> 00:11:01,710
What is this out of the blue?

177
00:11:01,710 --> 00:11:04,710
